Package: grafeoR
Title: R Bindings for the Grafeo Graph Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Raden Muhammad", "Hadi", , "31847323+hadimaster65555@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Raden Muhammad Hadi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Raden Muhammad Hadi <31847323+hadimaster65555@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: CRAN-first R bindings for the embedded Grafeo graph database,
    implemented in Rust via extendr and rextendr. The package provides an
    idiomatic R interface for opening in-memory or persistent Grafeo
    databases, executing GQL queries, and working with transactions.
URL: https://github.com/GrafeoDB/grafeo, https://grafeo.dev/
